{"tid":364471,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 美國上架RTS大作 Titanfall : Assault","createTime":"2017-08-18T11:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T09:40:51.000Z","uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4916118a045d4b10fed37d9ddb66171e444d307","tid":364471,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/194913_e003f576cc9f74ec8c1f5ef25f234309.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F194913_e003f576cc9f74ec8c1f5ef25f234309.jpg&h=f54f3c25&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/194937_80793dee1752ef524673eee96a1cbe00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F194937_80793dee1752ef524673eee96a1cbe00.jpg&h=0f2e5a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/195010_f9f56d573db43dd87900f2d2d5bf4d85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F195010_f9f56d573db43dd87900f2d2d5bf4d85.jpg&h=eea0efae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/195028_6b4c97f9c896d6e8d8d69360244ceb11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F195028_6b4c97f9c896d6e8d8d69360244ceb11.jpg&h=9ff873a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係家用機同電腦隻Titanfall嘅手機版game<br />\n常多人對戰槍game改到RTS玩法<br />\n一樣係節奏好高速有得空降Titan同步兵<br />\n放兵操作同升卡系統同皇室戰爭類似<br />\n但戰鬥玩落好唔同<br />\n個地圖有三個守據點<br />\n你霸左一個一陣就有1分<br />\n鬥快拎100分或打爆對方最後大炮塔就贏<br />\n打大炮塔前嘅中炮塔可擴展放兵範圍<br />\n<br />\nTitans唔識霸據點<br />\n唔識係建築物上行<br />\n會慢慢走向對方大炮塔<br />\n<br />\n步兵可霸據點<br />\n可以係建築物上行<br />\n或遊繩從高處落下（第二張地圖）<br />\n<br />\n以我個人玩左N場經驗<br />\n專心霸據點拎100分實際過打大炮塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同時守得住三個據點認真唔易<br />\n呢方面係難玩過皇室戰爭<br />\n<br />\nTitan初頭要等一陣先出到<br />\n步兵都有D特色<br />\n例如有D兵識係據點回體<br />\n<br />\nLv 3先有得用軍團功能<br />\nLv 5先開到第二張地圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔同地圖D據點同地形佈局有少少變化<br />\n例如第二張地圖有建築物可打爛行過去<br />\n新手玩認真要比D耐性升下Lv先多D地圖玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連線間唔中有bug<br />\n官方出公告有更新唔知有冇fix連線bug<br />\n所以我之前都費事太早出post<br />\n連線搵對手又認真等得耐<br />\n<br />\n日本同香港冇上架<br />\n所以你見到連登冇人提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得美國上架<br />\n如An版Google搵APK檔dl應該玩到<br />\n內置已有中文語言<br />\n<br />\n如果玩厭部落衝突同皇室戰爭同類玩法game<br />\n呢隻戰鬥都唔錯<br />\n幾有策略性同幾考即時判斷力黎霸三個據點<br />\n聲畫又幾好<br />\n<br />\n我開左個軍團叫LIHKG<br />\n大家自由join啦<br />\n係一個輕輕鬆鬆打機嘅軍團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會chur每個團員必要做乜<br />\n無乜必要唔會亂踢人走<br />\n亦唔得聞打理<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/18/194008_82c1ef34e1ec2cdbca0ef51224f7e490.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F18%2F194008_82c1ef34e1ec2cdbca0ef51224f7e490.jpg&h=9a366ac7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8a0ad1de18423209864c77b9e328946fa2c20287","tid":364471,"uid":134999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:11:14.000Z","msg":"比條link方便下巴絲們啦"},{"pid":"0209f288fa8270efbae523901f69022cad5859bc","tid":364471,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比條link方便下巴絲們啦</blockquote><br />\n美國App Store首頁新game<br />\n上高又有大banner<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAn版APK檔Google下就有"},{"pid":"686b8d478ec523cfa49a629fb125b7a54aadd307","tid":364471,"uid":24409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"睇落幾正 但無link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhk app store search 唔到？"},{"pid":"ec4496